Package: ynote
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Youngsik Yang <ynote@example.invalid>
Depends: python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0
Description: Engineer-friendly sticky notes for GNOME desktops
 Ynote is a lightweight GTK desktop notes app for Ubuntu and GNOME-based
 Linux desktops, with code blocks, images, search, formatting, and
 always-on-top notes.
